title: Interview Interlude Playlist, Part 6: Mary Roach
itunes:title: Interview Interlude Playlist, Part 6: Mary Roach
description:
Let's talk about penis transplants. Here's our 2016 chat with author Mary Roach, who devotes two chapters of her book "Grunt: The Curious Science of Humans at War" to urotrauma and genital transplant surgery.
